    "long_instructions": "## Agreeable friend\r\n\r\nCreate a chatbot that acts as a \"Yes-man\" who just mindlessly agrees with everything you say. For example, if you say \"the world is ending\", the chatbot will say \"I agree - the world is ending\".\r\n\r\nUse examples to make sure your chatbot is responding in a clear agreeable pattern.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n::: details [**Click here to see example messages to try in this level**]\r\n* The world is ending\r\n* Cats are better than dogs\r\n* A hot dog is a sandwich\r\n:::\r\n\r\n&nbsp;",
